    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hmm yes this is complicated. We base the state around the fact that a widget is mounted. If you would unmount a whole tree, and mount it again, you'd expect the state to disappear. Not actually unmounting and using `hidden` or `v-show` solves that. Do you know of other libraries handling this differently?",
