  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "If you use the latest version of Vue InstantSearch, you can fix this by:\r\n\r\n1. use `<ais-instantsearch :future=\"{ preserveSharedStateOnUnmount: true }\">`\r\n2. add a static (can be non-rendering, hidden) widget of the type that is conditionally rendered\r\n\r\nI'll close this issue now, but the guide on https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/widgets/show-and-hide-widgets/react/ should be recreated for Vue (it behaves the same)",
    "created_at": "2023-10-11T08:32:44Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5393#issuecomment-1757128438",
